[The preview is over!]

1290
01:05:31,260 --> 01:05:34,900
[It's time to make an actual short drama]

1291
01:05:35,410 --> 01:05:38,600
Create five episodes in total.

1292
01:05:38,600 --> 01:05:44,180
They will be judged in Rounds 3 and 4.

1293
01:05:44,180 --> 01:05:47,650
If you get eliminated in Round 3,

1294
01:05:47,650 --> 01:05:50,360
you cannot show the remaining episodes.

1295
01:05:50,360 --> 01:05:51,550
Huh?

1296
01:05:51,550 --> 01:05:54,780
[You can't show Episodes 3 to 5
if you get eliminated in Round 3]

1297
01:05:54,780 --> 01:05:57,560
- This is so cruel.
- That's rough.

1298
01:05:57,560 --> 01:06:01,120
There must be a reason for this rule.

1299
01:06:01,120 --> 01:06:05,720
The short drama market is very cutthroat.

1300
01:06:05,720 --> 01:06:09,740
Things get decided on episode 3 or 4.

1301
01:06:09,740 --> 01:06:12,050
Whether people would
turn it off or keep watching.

1302
01:06:12,050 --> 01:06:15,680
The number starts going down
starting in episode 3 or 4.

1303
01:06:15,680 --> 01:06:21,050
The rule reflects that. You could
say it's realistic and efficient.

1304
01:06:21,050 --> 01:06:23,400
It's exactly as you said.

1305
01:06:23,400 --> 01:06:27,360
This is the reality of a short drama.

1306
01:06:27,360 --> 01:06:29,690
It's the real ecosystem.

1307
01:06:29,690 --> 01:06:31,740
That's right. What do I do?

1308
01:06:32,650 --> 01:06:36,580
The directors are starting to look concerned.

1309
01:06:36,580 --> 01:06:38,830
What determines your survival?

1310
01:06:38,830 --> 01:06:42,450
You just have to defeat each other.

1311
01:06:42,450 --> 01:06:44,870
[Defeat each other?]

1312
01:06:44,870 --> 01:06:50,870
Round 3 will be 1:1 death matches.

1313
01:06:50,870 --> 01:06:53,970
[Cruel 1:1 death match where one drops out]

1314
01:06:53,970 --> 01:06:56,270
It's finally happening.

1315
01:06:56,270 --> 01:06:57,810
1:1...

1316
01:06:57,810 --> 01:07:01,070
I knew we'd be told to make five episodes.

1317
01:07:01,070 --> 01:07:04,830
But I didn't think it would be 1:1. It's too cruel.

1318
01:07:04,830 --> 01:07:07,270
I feel motivated for the first time.

1319
01:07:07,270 --> 01:07:09,160
I like to compete.

1320
01:07:09,870 --> 01:07:13,670
Now, how do we decide who they go up against?

1321
01:07:13,670 --> 01:07:15,830
There is only one way.

1322
01:07:15,830 --> 01:07:19,110
It will be "You, come out."

1323
01:07:19,110 --> 01:07:22,460
- You, come out.
- You, come out.

1324
01:07:22,460 --> 01:07:29,290
The Round 2's first-place team will choose first.

1325
01:07:29,290 --> 01:07:32,160
Who wants to go first?

1326
01:07:32,160 --> 01:07:35,730
Since I chose first last time...

1327
01:07:35,730 --> 01:07:37,290
[Ladies first]

1328
01:07:37,290 --> 01:07:40,180
Director Han Soo Ji will choose first.

1329
01:07:40,180 --> 01:07:43,020
Please come up on the stage.

1330
01:07:43,920 --> 01:07:45,700
Not me, not me.

1331
01:07:45,700 --> 01:07:47,700
I'll avoid eye contact.

1332
01:07:47,700 --> 01:07:49,690
[The first director they want
to avoid as an opponent]

1333
01:07:50,330 --> 01:07:53,810
[Everyone spoke highly
of Director Han Soo Ji's teaser]

1334
01:07:54,660 --> 01:07:58,970
[The first survivor who shocked everyone]

1335
01:07:59,400 --> 01:08:02,820
Director Han Soo Ji,

1336
01:08:02,820 --> 01:08:04,500
pick your opponent.

1337
01:08:04,500 --> 01:08:06,310
Gosh, seriously.

1338
01:08:06,310 --> 01:08:09,600
[Avoiding eye contact]

1339
01:08:10,360 --> 01:08:16,740
This person talked about
"Snakes and Ladders" a lot.

1340
01:08:16,740 --> 01:08:18,690
[Who praised "Snakes and Ladders"?]

1341
01:08:18,690 --> 01:08:22,500
Lee Joo Seung, come out.

1342
01:08:22,500 --> 01:08:25,680
She picked Director Lee Joo Seung.

1343
01:08:25,680 --> 01:08:28,920
[Why did I have to do that?]

1344
01:08:29,200 --> 01:08:30,550
[Sigh]

1345
01:08:30,550 --> 01:08:32,700
The actors are busy.

1346
01:08:32,700 --> 01:08:36,930
I thought I'd have more time than him.

1347
01:08:36,930 --> 01:08:38,350
[The first death match pair]

1348
01:08:38,690 --> 01:08:40,530
[Hehe]

1349
01:08:40,530 --> 01:08:43,620
[Dizzy]

1350
01:08:43,620 --> 01:08:46,560
You got a powerful opponent.

1351
01:08:46,560 --> 01:08:49,030
I didn't think it would be me.

1352
01:08:49,030 --> 01:08:51,660
I feel so devastated.

1353
01:08:51,660 --> 01:08:54,420
While in the green room just now,

1354
01:08:54,420 --> 01:08:57,320
she asked me if I would work with her, too.

1355
01:08:57,320 --> 01:08:58,620
So, I said I would love to.

1356
01:08:58,620 --> 01:09:00,510
She said, "I'll let you fly."

1357
01:09:00,510 --> 01:09:02,810
But she stabbed me with a shovel instead.

1358
01:09:02,810 --> 01:09:06,940
How could she betray me like this?

1359
01:09:06,940 --> 01:09:12,580
I'm sorry, but I will end up
in the next round. Thank you.

1360
01:09:12,580 --> 01:09:16,090
I'll make you fall from "Snakes and Ladders."

1361
01:09:16,090 --> 01:09:17,900
You'll see.

1362
01:09:20,030 --> 01:09:23,000
[Lee Joo Seung vs. Han Soo Ji]

1363
01:09:23,560 --> 01:09:25,060
Director Lee Yoo Jin.

1364
01:09:25,060 --> 01:09:28,090
What's that? He's making eye contact.

1365
01:09:28,090 --> 01:09:29,550
Don't do it. Don't do it. Don't do it.

1366
01:09:29,550 --> 01:09:31,710
Director Han Sang Il just...

1367
01:09:31,710 --> 01:09:33,800
I hope he doesn't pick me.

1368
01:09:34,770 --> 01:09:36,780
I didn't care who it would be.

1369
01:09:36,780 --> 01:09:40,440
You could say he's a potential winner.

1370
01:09:42,620 --> 01:09:45,930
Go Hyeon Guk, come out.

1371
01:09:45,930 --> 01:09:48,580
Go Hyeon Guk, come out.

1372
01:09:48,580 --> 01:09:51,300
- Wow.
- Director Go Hyeon Guk.

1373
01:09:51,300 --> 01:09:52,610
[Walking to hell calmly]

1374
01:09:52,610 --> 01:09:54,840
Show Me the Money.

1375
01:09:54,840 --> 01:09:57,930
[An unexpected pairing]

1376
01:09:58,400 --> 01:10:00,760
Is there a reason you chose him?

1377
01:10:02,150 --> 01:10:03,930
Because I'm easy?

1378
01:10:03,930 --> 01:10:05,570
I can't really remember.

1379
01:10:05,570 --> 01:10:06,680
What do you mean?

1380
01:10:06,680 --> 01:10:08,250
His teaser.

1381
01:10:08,250 --> 01:10:10,420
[Starting with a provocation]

1382
01:10:10,420 --> 01:10:13,430
[Dopamine rush]

1383
01:10:13,430 --> 01:10:15,230
Mic drop.

1384
01:10:16,130 --> 01:10:20,060
To be honest, I don't really
remember his story, either.

1385
01:10:20,060 --> 01:10:22,060
What was it about?

1386
01:10:22,060 --> 01:10:23,760
I remember him running around.

1387
01:10:23,760 --> 01:10:26,080
His father was in it, too.

1388
01:10:26,080 --> 01:10:28,470
But I don't really remember the story.

1389
01:10:29,320 --> 01:10:30,890
You don't remember?

1390
01:10:30,890 --> 01:10:32,750
He's like, "Who are you?"

1391
01:10:32,750 --> 01:10:35,670
Director Han Soo Ji is shocked.

1392
01:10:35,670 --> 01:10:40,330
- She's like, "Is that who he is?"
- He was a scary person.

1393
01:10:41,630 --> 01:10:46,230
I can't pretend to remember it.

1394
01:10:46,230 --> 01:10:48,150
[Go Hyeon Guk vs. Lee Yoo Jin]

1395
01:10:48,150 --> 01:10:52,360
The second-place directors,
Han Sang Il and Jeong Joo.

1396
01:10:52,360 --> 01:10:54,000
Huh? Is that what you're doing?

1397
01:10:54,000 --> 01:10:57,170
You played rock-paper-scissors? That's fair.

1398
01:10:58,670 --> 01:11:01,670
It won't matter who I choose.

1399
01:11:01,670 --> 01:11:03,150
[Who will be chosen?]

1400
01:11:04,580 --> 01:11:08,270
- You never know what will happen.
- It won't be easy.

1401
01:11:08,270 --> 01:11:10,990
I'll make you a variety show star.

1402
01:11:10,990 --> 01:11:13,920
- Huh?
- Who is it?

1403
01:11:13,920 --> 01:11:15,970
Director Jeong Joo, come out.

1404
01:11:17,540 --> 01:11:20,230
[LOL]

1405
01:11:20,230 --> 01:11:21,670
[This is a short drama]

1406
01:11:21,670 --> 01:11:23,950
This is fun. This is fun.

1407
01:11:23,950 --> 01:11:26,030
[This will be entertaining]

1408
01:11:26,760 --> 01:11:32,710
We've been teasing Director Han Sang Il a lot.

1409
01:11:32,710 --> 01:11:34,840
I admire this decision.

1410
01:11:34,840 --> 01:11:37,570
Today's partner is tomorrow's enemy.

1411
01:11:37,570 --> 01:11:39,880
I have nothing to criticize. I loved it.

1412
01:11:39,880 --> 01:11:42,430
It makes you want to watch it again.

1413
01:11:42,430 --> 01:11:44,910
I even thought I'd like to work with you.

1414
01:11:44,910 --> 01:11:46,880
[The war for the perfect
Team "Black Out Girl Hanami"]

1415
01:11:46,880 --> 01:11:49,340
I didn't see that coming at all.

1416
01:11:49,340 --> 01:11:50,870
I was wondering who he would choose.

1417
01:11:50,870 --> 01:11:52,960
He picked me from the back?

1418
01:11:52,960 --> 01:11:56,200
I chose him in the last round
because he's nothing like me.

1419
01:11:56,200 --> 01:11:57,690
I thought that would let me shine.

1420
01:11:57,690 --> 01:11:59,450
I learned a lot from him.

1421
01:11:59,450 --> 01:12:01,740
This will be like mirror therapy.

1422
01:12:01,740 --> 01:12:03,810
I hope you're ready.

1423
01:12:03,900 --> 01:12:07,300
Since we're enemies now, I hope you fail.

1424
01:12:07,340 --> 01:12:09,670
[Jeong Joo vs. Han Sang Il]

1425
01:12:09,670 --> 01:12:13,360
Next is the third-place director, Lee Dong Hun.

1426
01:12:13,360 --> 01:12:16,460
I choose director Yun Hyeong Shik.

1427
01:12:17,450 --> 01:12:22,010
Directors Park So Rang and Yang Gyeong Hee
are paired up automatically.

1428
01:12:22,830 --> 01:12:26,500
I'll crush him with the result.

1429
01:12:26,500 --> 01:12:28,010
He'll have to work hard.

1430
01:12:28,010 --> 01:12:30,760
Because I'm really determined.

1431
01:12:30,760 --> 01:12:32,720
I'll win.

1432
01:12:32,720 --> 01:12:36,550
I'll show you why I'm the
No. 1 short drama director.

1433
01:12:36,550 --> 01:12:38,380
So cool. So cool.

1434
01:12:38,380 --> 01:12:42,360
I had a number one series, too.

1435
01:12:43,230 --> 01:12:49,290
Round 3 is 1:1 death matches
where only one of the two survives.

1436
01:12:49,290 --> 01:12:50,840
[Round 3 finally starts]

1437
01:12:50,840 --> 01:12:52,930
It was easy to copy him.

1438
01:12:52,930 --> 01:12:54,580
It's not something you can just copy.

1439
01:12:54,580 --> 01:12:56,620
Wow. More, more, more!

1440
01:12:56,620 --> 01:12:59,900
This will be your last time on stage.

1441
01:12:59,900 --> 01:13:02,570
- This is more fun than shorts.
- This is "Show Me the Money."

1442
01:13:02,570 --> 01:13:03,790
[The short drama war got even more exciting]

1443
01:13:04,520 --> 01:13:06,220
Move.

1444
01:13:06,220 --> 01:13:07,490
[More fun]

1445
01:13:09,050 --> 01:13:09,980
[Creepier]

1446
01:13:11,680 --> 01:13:13,680
[And more provocative!]

1447
01:13:13,680 --> 01:13:15,210
[Who will survive?]

1448
01:13:16,130 --> 01:13:18,730
The judging is ruthless today.

1449
01:13:18,730 --> 01:13:20,850
It was disappointing and chaotic.

1450
01:13:20,850 --> 01:13:22,420
It's too much.

1451
01:13:22,420 --> 01:13:24,320
I thought I'd get a heart attack.

1452
01:13:24,320 --> 01:13:26,890
It felt like my blood was drying.

1453
01:13:26,890 --> 01:13:28,650
[An underdog's rebellion?]

1454
01:13:29,090 --> 01:13:31,750
Director Han Soo Ji must be terrified.

1455
01:13:31,750 --> 01:13:33,240
I thought I was screwed.

1456
01:13:33,240 --> 01:13:36,920
You are a different person than
in the previous round.

1457
01:13:36,920 --> 01:13:39,520
It's about time for me to win.

1458
01:13:39,520 --> 01:13:40,760
I think I'll win.

1459
01:13:40,760 --> 01:13:43,470
[Who will have the last laugh?]
